OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772447794
OL,3,CRat activity shows significant
OL,4,Cincrease after hot summer and recent
OL,5,Crain
OL,7,FRentokil warned that the record-
OL,8,Fbreaking wet start to 2026 across the
OL,9,FUK could also lead to higher levels of
OL,10,Frat activity.
OL,12,FSustained heavy rain can flood burrow
OL,13,Fsystems and drainage networks,
OL,14,Fdisplacing rats and increasing the
OL,15,Flikelihood of infestations as they
OL,16,Fseek higher, drier shelter, it said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
