OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772447794
OL,3,CRat activity shows significant
OL,4,Cincrease after hot summer and recent
OL,5,Crain
OL,7,F"With northern regions already
OL,8,Freporting notable increases in
OL,9,Freported activity, continued wet
OL,10,Fweather may push more rats into
OL,11,Fproperties. Early prevention and
OL,12,Fprofessional support are key.
OL,14,F"Simple steps such as proofing entry
OL,15,Fpoints, managing waste effectively and
OL,16,Fresponding quickly to early signs of
OL,17,Factivity can make a significant
OL,18,Fdifference. If a problem does become
OL,19,Funmanageable, professional pest
OL,20,Fcontrol experts are always on hand to
OL,21,Fprovide safe and effective solutions."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
